uC++ Syntax Highlighting for Vim
--------------------------------

Highlight uC++ source code contained in '.ucpp' or '.uh' files.

Installation
------------

Assume your downloaded (and unzipped) copy is located in the directory `ucpp-vim-syntax`.

### Option 1: Manual Installation

Copy the sub-directories of `ucpp-vim-syntax` into `~/.vim/`:

    cp -r ucpp-vim-syntax/ftdetect ~/.vim/
    cp -r ucpp-vim-syntax/syntax ~/.vim/

### Option 2: Pathogen Installation

1. Download and install Pathogen (https://github.com/tpope/vim-pathogen).
2. Move:

        mv ucpp-vim-syntax ~/.vim/bundle/
